esofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132140093.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/indian-passport-fees-in-uae-revised-from-july-1-check-new-charges-for-fresh-tatkaal-applications/articleshow/132140093.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/indian-passport-fees-in-uae-revised-from-july-1-check-new-charges-for-fresh-tatkaal-applications/articleshow/132140093.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-02T19:11:12+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132140288,imgsize-106804.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[More than 1,200 hectares burnt! Firefighters battle southern France wildfires after deadly heatwave]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132139464.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[On Thursday, southern France faced intense wildfires that scorched more than 1,200 hectares, ignited by strong winds and dry conditions following a severe heatwave. The most significant blaze occurred in Aude, close to Spain, devouring 900 hectares. Firefighters, supported by water-bombing aircraft, fought bravely to control the situation, and thankfully, no casualties have been reported.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/more-than-1200-hectares-of-land-burnt-firefighters-battle-southern-france-wildfires-after-deadly-heatwave/articleshow/132139464.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/more-than-1200-hectares-of-land-burnt-firefighters-battle-southern-france-wildfires-after-deadly-heatwave/articleshow/132139464.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-02T18:12:21+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="